    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools of various designs used for cutting glass by scoring a line on a piece of glass. The scoring makes a split in the surface of the glass, allowing the glass to be snapped or broken along the score.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
